subject: Basketball
College Athletics
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: LaQuita Owens scored a season-high 23 points and No. 12 West Virginia used a 21-4 run in the second half to beat No. 4 Rutgers, 63-54, on Tuesday night.
